ca.uqac.lif.ecp.statechart.atomic

Class AtomicStatechartBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.statechart.atomic.AtomicStatechartBuilder

  • public class AtomicStatechartBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a statechart of atomic events out of a text string. The statechart must be structured as follows.
    • The statechart is enclosed between the lines begin statechart and end statechart
    • The states are declared in a section begin states … end states
    • The transitions are declared in a section begin transitions … end transitions
    Author:
    Sylvain Hallé
